{"tid":1620866,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一場革命需要準備嘅嘢有好多","createTime":"2019-10-04T11:39:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T11:46:56.000Z","uid":238801,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1ec70de66648816bb73ad3d8ba73ac7674fb754c","tid":1620866,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:39:47.000Z","msg":"首先革命即係要推翻現有政權<br />\n成立新政府<br />\n當中所需求嘅係全香港人團結同必勝嘅心<br />\n同埋需要有目的有部署一步步去令到政府收皮<br />\n然後臨時政府完全取締舊政府<br />\n先有可能達成到我地嘅訴求<br />\n<br />\n香港人 若然真係革命的話 你地一定要準備好心理<br />\n呢場係一場必需取勝嘅戰爭<br />\n時間可能需要幾十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我希望大家唔好一頭熱血就行動 行動之前要諗清楚我地革命嘅目的係推翻乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推翻港共 香港獨立</span><br />\n利申好掛住梁天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要成功只有獨立呢條路呀<br />\n現存嘅行政架構冇可能做到我地想要嘅嘢"},{"pid":"a6f36726aa8488c38a823f2925e61454dc7e355a","tid":1620866,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:40:38.000Z","msg":"心態好重要"},{"pid":"2f6cfd432a642a8211b7bd4f496f1fb4548278e7","tid":1620866,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:40:46.000Z","msg":"要勇武既心"},{"pid":"0588f22777b989bba9c2670fe3b2a07e45c4bacb","tid":1620866,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:41:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38f519842154e7d7352ad25fcbe6ef0103de3a9","tid":1620866,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:46:14.000Z","msg":"仲等咩"},{"pid":"1a9816aae905fc2d48cff9a778e3caf58399c260","tid":1620866,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:46:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33049f7e55494ea90e4ff40f4b1ec66